## Environment Variables Template
## Copy this file to `.env` (optional) and adjust values as needed.
## Never commit `.env` to version control.

## API runtime configuration (required for API demo)
MODEL_PATH=models/distilmbert_lora_10k_v1.pt
THRESHOLDS_PATH=config/thresholds.json

## Dashboards -> API (optional)
## - Local (running API on your machine): http://localhost:8000
## - Docker Compose dashboards talking to API service: http://api:8000
API_URL=http://localhost:8000

## Tokenizer override (optional; normally inferred from checkpoint)
TOKENIZER_NAME=distilbert-base-multilingual-cased

## Weights & Biases (optional; training only)
# WANDB_API_KEY=...
# WANDB_PROJECT=russian-news-classification
# WANDB_ENTITY=...

